---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: 'Project Planning & Consulting',
  provider: { '@type': 'GeneralContractor', name: 'Purpose Construction', url: 'https://purposeconstructionco.com' },
  areaServed: { '@type': 'State', name: 'Texas', containedIn: { '@type': 'Country', name: 'United States' } },
  description: 'Project planning and consulting for East Texas homeowners — scope development, budget planning, timeline building, permit guidance, and contractor coordination for construction and remodeling projects across East Texas.',
};
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Project Planning & Consulting East Texas | Purpose Construction"
  description="Construction project planning and consulting across East Texas — scope, budget, timeline, and permit guidance for East Texas homeowners planning to build or remodel. Call (936) 555-5555."
  schema={schema}
>
  <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: 'Services', href: '/services' }, { label: 'Project Planning & Consulting', href: '/project-planning-consulting' }]} />
  <PageHero title="Project Planning & Consulting in East Texas" subtitle="Know what your project involves, what it costs, and how to get from idea to finished build — before you ever break ground." tag="General Service" />

  <section class="section-padding bg-warm-50">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
        <div>
          <SectionHeading tag="Project Planning" title="The Clarity You Need Before Construction Starts" />
          <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-charcoal-600">
            <p>Most construction problems start long before the first nail is driven — in the planning phase, when a project scope isn't clearly defined, a budget isn't realistic, or a homeowner doesn't fully understand what they're committing to. Purpose Construction offers project planning and consulting services for East Texas homeowners who want to approach their build or remodel with a clear, informed plan rather than figuring it out under pressure mid-project.</p>
            <p>We sit down with you, walk through what you're trying to accomplish, and help you build a realistic scope, a grounded budget, and a sequenced timeline. For projects requiring permits in Angelina County or the City of Lufkin, we guide you through what's required and how to navigate the process. If your project involves multiple contractors, we help you understand how the trades sequence and what to look for when you're evaluating bids and selecting subs.</p>
            <p>Consulting doesn't require committing to a full build with us. If you're in the early stages of planning and just need experienced guidance, that's a valid use of our time. Many homeowners find that an hour of honest planning conversation saves them months of costly miscommunication down the road.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 flex gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation</a>
            <a href="/services" class="btn-outline">All Services</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img src="https://placehold.co/640x480/2a2520/555?text=Project+Planning" alt="Project planning and consulting across East Texas by Purpose Construction" class="rounded-xl shadow-hero" width="640" height="480" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-white border-t border-warm-200">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading tag="What's Included" title="Planning & Consulting Services" align="center" />
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4">
        {['Scope Development', 'Budget Planning', 'Timeline Building', 'Permit Guidance', 'Contractor Coordination', 'Material Sourcing', 'Site Assessment', 'Phased Project Planning'].map(item => (
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-warm-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-charcoal-700">
            <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand-red" aria-hidden="true"></span>{item}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding-sm bg-warm-50 border-t border-warm-200">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading tag="Related Services" title="Related Services" />
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        {[{ label: 'Site Preparation', href: '/site-preparation' }, { label: 'All Services', href: '/services' }].map(link => (
          <a href={link.href} class="rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-charcoal-700 shadow-card hover:border-brand-red-mid hover:text-charcoal-900 transition-all duration-200">{link.label} →</a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-red">
    <div class="container-mid px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="display-md text-white mb-4">Start With a Conversation</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-xl text-base text-white/80">Contact Purpose Construction to schedule a project planning consultation. We help East Texas homeowners build with confidence from day one.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-ghost px-8 py-4">Schedule a Consultation</a>
        <a href="tel:9365555555" class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150">(936) 555-5555</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
